        {
            "_id": "DzuUUmbM8O50g566",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Get 'em!",
            "sort": 400000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> to <span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span></p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The mercenary squad engages in a coordinated melee attack against each adjacent enemy, with a @Check[reflex|dc:15|basic] save. The damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[(1d6+2)[bludgeoning]] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(1d6+5)[bludgeoning]] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(1d6+8)[bludgeoning]] damage</p>"
                },
